requirement_designation: Humanities and Arts with Race & Ethnicity(*)
course_description: This course is an introduction to the study of women, gender, and sexuality. Syllabus materials will explore the ways in which these systems of social classification are shaped by race, ethnicity, class, ability, and nation.
